{
  "stem": "597.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "There was no fire in the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "The only fire we put up is to cook a potato.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Cold.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The winter from '41, '42, was the worst winter I had in my life-- in my lifetime.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Cold, hungry, undernourished.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We had my mother's mother came in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Was staying with us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "The older person, 82 years old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "The only thing we could give her to eat is a piece of potato.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And that-- that winter, she died from hunger.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Winter until summertime.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Then was springtime.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Springtime was the big, '42, was the big roundup, the killing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And my grandmother died Pesach, that was April, before the killing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the working.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whether you work [INAUDIBLE] before the roundup was, most of the time, the Ukrainian people helped the people, the Nationalist.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- they want to have their own country, you know, separate-- a separate Ukraine, not to belong to the Russia, to somebody else.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So these people came out, and they are, was ruling.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was not too many of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just the village surround.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "These people came out, and they did terrible things to us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Terrible things the did to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They-- they find out all the Jews, where they are.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They-- they rounded up Jews, helped to round up Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Whatever the Germans told them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They helped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They helped the German government to do it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because they didn't, the German didn't know who was a Jew, who's not a Jew.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They told them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The Ukrainian people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The teacher, what was teaching us at school, [INAUDIBLE], he was the-- he was a little bit in the government there, too, but later on didn't agree with them, they-- he backed up.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
